{"tid":1079473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[瘟疫] 美紐約市郊爆麻疹疫情進入緊急狀態","createTime":"2019-03-27T03:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T05:20:14.000Z","uid":51620,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8ba08344d4b088db4655dcab93a90e62a7c35197","tid":1079473,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T03:27:43.000Z","msg":"美紐約市郊爆麻疹疫情進入緊急狀態<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=342342&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D342342%26refer%3DShare&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5YbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=91fc2e33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D342342%26refer%3DShare&h=f07582a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=342342&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"007c06f3ec6d8b1e2a74528dd69292f06cfa0b7e","tid":1079473,"uid":131717,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T03:29:01.000Z","msg":"反疫苗撚又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e785a0d02153003cfb7b4167d4ec9cb2a786ccd","tid":1079473,"uid":51620,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T03:29:04.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國東岸麻疹疫情不斷擴散，紐約市疫情嚴重，市郊羅克蘭縣至少150人已確診感染，當局宣布進入緊急狀態，並禁止未有接種麻疹疫苗的兒童進出公眾場所，保障他們的健康。<br />\n<br />\n縣政府指一旦發現有兒童未接種疫苗便出入公眾場所，家長須負上刑責，至於身體不適宜接種疫苗的未成年人士獲當局確認理由後可獲豁免，但宗教信仰或認為疫苗引發自閉症均不是豁免理由，多個科學研究均顯示接種疫苗與自閉症並無聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n羅克蘭縣的疫情去年十月開始，七名確診感染麻疹的旅客進入該縣，他們都無接種過麻疹疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n今個月較早時候，聯邦法官亦拒絕家長讓44名未有接種疫苗的子女返回位於羅克蘭縣的學校上學。"},{"pid":"8566bcbab5fb3a817d8d325a23fd355a073295d3","tid":1079473,"uid":51620,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"007c06f3ec6d8b1e2a74528dd69292f06cfa0b7e","tid":1079473,"uid":131717,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-